Video shows how John Moynihan, 34, was shot within seconds of opening Angelo West's car door . 
 West, 41, immediately jumps out of the car and shoots the officer . 
 Video then shows West shooting at officers as he runs across the street . 
 West was fatally shot by Moynihan's colleagues during the shoot-out . 
 Police said they released the video to be transparent with the public and tamp down rumors . 
 Moynihan was released from the hospital Friday after weeks of recovery . 
 Police said his current condition is 'serious but improving'